{
  "stem": "21008.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My father opened the door with the first Russian soldier.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my father knew some Russian, spoke to him, told him who we were, who he is, and that his family is there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this Russian soldier was also Jewish, and they embraced.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- the-- this Russian soldier right away informed his commander that there's a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the commander came, who was a tall, handsome guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A-- a-- a Tartar?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "An Asian type.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know, actually, where he was from.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he right away sorted the cellar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, 3/4 of the cellar was for the Jewish family, and the others were all pushed in one tiny little corner, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was tough on them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We got food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He gave us water from-- from their army supplies, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Saw to it that we are safe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He watched me like a hawk, because soldiers rape women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was 17 years old, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he watched me like a hawk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, I really have to thank him that nothing happened to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That lasted about 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the fighting was still fierce.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They hadn't-- they couldn't progress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we had to all out into the courtyard of the building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, the building was half destroyed by now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were all lined up in the courtyard, and they put up machine guns.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, there goes my young life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was ready--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
